<plot>'Whole' is a neo-noir crime-drama about a cop named Leon who has everything going for him. He is engaged to a beautiful and smart woman, Jane and he is on his way to being promoted to chief of police. Gary, a fellow officer and friend to Leon, creates a scene at Leon and Jane's engagement party and ruins the evening. Leon's fortune suddenly begins to change. When Leon approaches Gary in private, Gary confesses that he is still in love with Leon and cannot cope with Leon's decision to get married to Jane. Regardless of Gary's feelings Leon breaks it off for good. The next time Leon see's Gary, he is in a body bag; murdered. Its only when Leon comes face to face with Gary's murderer that his morals and values will be put to the test.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?655507</url></doc>
